snippet.title: Horror Game Trailer - Gift Collector [ギフトコレクター]
snippet.description: Gift Collector [ギフトコレクター] - this is a New Year's horror game from the first person, in the Japanese style and genre of walking simulator. Collect gifts and make the kids happy on New Year's Eve. But don't forget that Midnight is a time of miracles!
